pomProject.name: jlayer-libgdx
pomProject.description: Jlayer version used in libgdx. Fixed some NPEs, changed how buffering happens, deleted most of the classes, everything not related to decoding and half of what was related to decoding but not needed. Added support for reading replay gain out of the mp3.

pomProject.name: Pure Java Ogg Vorbis Decoder
pomProject.description: JOrbis accepts Ogg Vorbis bitstreams and decodes them to raw PCM.

pomProject.name: minimalcode-beans
pomProject.description: Minimalistic high-level wrapper functionality for JavaBean

pomProject.name: minimalcode-reflect
pomProject.description: Minimalistic reflection and introspection functionality for JavaBean
